### MERN Stack Backend API Testing
### Use REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tool

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================

### 1. Initiate Google OAuth (Open in browser)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/google

### 2. Get Current User (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Logout (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
