GET {{baseUrl}}/friends
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 16. Check if Friends
GET {{baseUrl}}/friends/check/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### CHAT
### ============================================

### 17. Send Message (Friends Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/message
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
