### ============================================
### NOTES
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Replace {{token}} with actual JWT token from Google OAuth callback
### 2. Replace USER_ID_HERE, POST_ID_HERE, REQUEST_ID_HERE with actual IDs
### 3. For file uploads, use actual file paths
### 4. All protected routes require Authorization header with Bearer token
### 5. Google OAuth flow:
###    - GET /auth/google (redirects to Google)
###    - Google redirects to /auth/google/callback
###    - Callback redirects to frontend with token
###    - Use token in Authorization header for protected routes
###
